  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca - \u0db6\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0db1\u0d9f\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The price of bread and buns is rising",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the increase in the price of wheat flour, bakery owners have taken steps to increase the prices of bakery products including bread.",
        "Accordingly, the price of a loaf of bread will have to be increased by 20 rupees from midnight today (12) and the price of other bakery products by 10 rupees, said N. Mr. K. Jayawardene stated.",
        "The Association of Bakery Owners says that this decision was taken because Prima Company increased the price of bread flour by 34 rupees. Accordingly, the current price of a kilo of bread is 300 rupees.",
        "Accordingly, he said, the new price of a pound of paddy will be between 190 and 210 rupees."
      ],
